The paper discusses the design of a blockchain-based decentralized trustless API marketplace, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR), distributed systems (cs.DC), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The system also involves software engineering aspects such as designing and implementing a decentralized system (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with AI models and APIs.
